{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Rom|2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","chapter":2,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v10","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":1,"text":"Therefore, every one of you who judges is without excuse. For when you judge another, you condemn yourself, since you, the judge, do the same things.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":2,"text":"Now we know that God’s judgment on those who do such things is based on the truth.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":3,"text":"Do you think —anyone of you who judges those who do such things yet do the same —that you will escape God’s judgment?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":4,"text":"Or do you despise the riches of his kindness, restraint, and patience, not recognizing that God’s kindness is intended to lead you to repentance?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":5,"text":"Because of your hardened and unrepentant heart you are storing up wrath for yourself in the day of wrath, when God’s righteous judgment is revealed.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":6,"text":"He will repay each one according to his works:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":7,"text":"eternal life to those who by persistence in doing good seek glory, honor, and immortality;","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":8,"text":"but wrath and anger to those who are self-seeking and disobey the truth while obeying unrighteousness.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":9,"text":"There will be affliction and distress for every human being who does evil, first to the Jew, and also to the Greek;","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":10,"text":"but glory, honor, and peace for everyone who does what is good, first to the Jew, and also to the Greek.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":11,"text":"For there is no favoritism with God.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":12,"text":"For all who sin without the law will also perish without the law, and all who sin under the law will be judged by the law.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":13,"text":"For the hearers of the law are not righteous before God, but the doers of the law will be justified.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":14,"text":"So, when Gentiles, who do not by nature have the law, do what the law demands, they are a law to themselves even though they do not have the law.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":15,"text":"They show that the work of the law is written on their hearts. Their consciences confirm this. Their competing thoughts either accuse or even excuse them","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":16,"text":"on the day when God judges what people have kept secret, according to my gospel through Christ Jesus.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":17,"text":"Now if you call yourself a Jew, and rely on the law, and boast in God,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:18","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":18,"text":"and know his will, and approve the things that are superior, being instructed from the law,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:19","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":19,"text":"and if you are convinced that you are a guide for the blind, a light to those in darkness,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:20","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":20,"text":"an instructor of the ignorant, a teacher of the immature, having the embodiment of knowledge and truth in the law —","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:21","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":21,"text":"you then, who teach another, don’t you teach yourself? You who preach, “You must not steal” —do you steal?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:22","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":22,"text":"You who say, “You must not commit adultery” —do you commit adultery? You who detest idols, do you rob temples?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:23","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":23,"text":"You who boast in the law, do you dishonor God by breaking the law?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:24","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":24,"text":"For, as it is written: The name of God is blasphemed among the Gentiles because of you.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:25","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":25,"text":"Circumcision benefits you if you observe the law, but if you are a lawbreaker, your circumcision has become uncircumcision.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:26","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":26,"text":"So if an uncircumcised man keeps the law’s requirements, will not his uncircumcision be counted as circumcision?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:27","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":27,"text":"A man who is physically uncircumcised, but who keeps the law, will judge you who are a lawbreaker in spite of having the letter of the law and circumcision.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:28","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":28,"text":"For a person is not a Jew who is one outwardly, and true circumcision is not something visible in the flesh.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:29","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":2,"verse":29,"text":"On the contrary, a person is a Jew who is one inwardly, and circumcision is of the heart —by the Spirit, not the letter. That person’s praise is not from people but from God.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","chapter":2,"paragraphStarts":[1,12,17,25],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"God’s Righteous Judgment"},{"beforeVerse":17,"text":"Jewish Violation of the Law"},{"beforeVerse":25,"text":"Circumcision of the Heart"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore, every one of you "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit Therefore, O man, every one"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 12:14","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 9:20","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":20,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" who judges is without excuse. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:20","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":20,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" For when you judge another, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Sm 12:5","book":"2Sa","chapter":12,"verse":5,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 7:1","book":"Mat","chapter":7,"verse":1,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 14:22","book":"Rom","chapter":14,"verse":22,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" you condemn yourself, since you, the judge, do the same things. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 12:14","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":14},{"label":"Rm 9:20","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":20},{"label":"Rm 1:20","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":20},{"label":"2Sm 12:5","book":"2Sa","chapter":12,"verse":5},{"label":"Mt 7:1","book":"Mat","chapter":7,"verse":1},{"label":"Rm 14:22","book":"Rom","chapter":14,"verse":22}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit Therefore, O man, every one"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:2","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now we know that God’s judgment on those who do such things is based on the truth. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:3","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Do you think —anyone of you who judges those who do such things yet do the same —that you will escape God’s judgment? "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Or do you despise the riches of his kindness, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 11:22","book":"Rom","chapter":11,"verse":22,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" restraint, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 3:25","book":"Rom","chapter":3,"verse":25,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" and patience, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 34:6","book":"Exo","chapter":34,"verse":6,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 9:22","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":22,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 1:16","book":"1Ti","chapter":1,"verse":16,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 3:20","book":"1Pe","chapter":3,"verse":20,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Pt 3:15","book":"2Pe","chapter":3,"verse":15,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" not recognizing "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or patience, because you do not recognize"},{"kind":"text","text":" that God’s kindness "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Pt 3:9","book":"2Pe","chapter":3,"verse":9,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" is intended to lead you to repentance? "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 11:22","book":"Rom","chapter":11,"verse":22},{"label":"Rm 3:25","book":"Rom","chapter":3,"verse":25},{"label":"Ex 34:6","book":"Exo","chapter":34,"verse":6},{"label":"Rm 9:22","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":22},{"label":"1Tm 1:16","book":"1Ti","chapter":1,"verse":16},{"label":"1Pt 3:20","book":"1Pe","chapter":3,"verse":20},{"label":"2Pt 3:15","book":"2Pe","chapter":3,"verse":15},{"label":"2Pt 3:9","book":"2Pe","chapter":3,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Or patience, because you do not recognize"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Because of your hardened and unrepentant heart you are storing up wrath "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 32:34","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":34,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 1:18","book":"Pro","chapter":1,"verse":18,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" for yourself in the day of wrath, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 110:5","book":"Psa","chapter":110,"verse":5,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 5:10","book":"2Co","chapter":5,"verse":10,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Th 1:5","book":"2Th","chapter":1,"verse":5,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jd 1:6","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":6,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" when God’s righteous judgment is revealed. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 32:34","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":34},{"label":"Pr 1:18","book":"Pro","chapter":1,"verse":18},{"label":"Ps 110:5","book":"Psa","chapter":110,"verse":5},{"label":"2Co 5:10","book":"2Co","chapter":5,"verse":10},{"label":"2Th 1:5","book":"2Th","chapter":1,"verse":5},{"label":"Jd 1:6","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He will repay each one according to his works: "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 62:12","book":"Psa","chapter":62,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 24:12","book":"Pro","chapter":24,"verse":12,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 62:12","book":"Psa","chapter":62,"verse":12,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 24:12","book":"Pro","chapter":24,"verse":12,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 16:27","book":"Mat","chapter":16,"verse":27,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 62:12","book":"Psa","chapter":62,"verse":12},{"label":"Pr 24:12","book":"Pro","chapter":24,"verse":12},{"label":"Ps 62:12","book":"Psa","chapter":62,"verse":12},{"label":"Pr 24:12","book":"Pro","chapter":24,"verse":12},{"label":"Mt 16:27","book":"Mat","chapter":16,"verse":27}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"eternal life "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 15:42","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":42,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 15:50","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":50,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 15:53","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":53,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" to those who by persistence in doing good "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 8:15","book":"Luk","chapter":8,"verse":15,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 10:36","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":36,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" seek glory, honor, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 2:7","book":"Heb","chapter":2,"verse":7,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 1:7","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":7,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" and immortality; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 25:46","book":"Mat","chapter":25,"verse":46,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 15:42","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":42},{"label":"1Co 15:50","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":50},{"label":"1Co 15:53","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":53},{"label":"Lk 8:15","book":"Luk","chapter":8,"verse":15},{"label":"Heb 10:36","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":36},{"label":"Heb 2:7","book":"Heb","chapter":2,"verse":7},{"label":"1Pt 1:7","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":7},{"label":"Mt 25:46","book":"Mat","chapter":25,"verse":46}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"but wrath and anger to those who are self-seeking "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 12:20","book":"2Co","chapter":12,"verse":20,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 5:20","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":20,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 2:3","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":3,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 3:14","book":"Jas","chapter":3,"verse":14,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 3:16","book":"Jas","chapter":3,"verse":16,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" and disobey the truth "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Th 2:12","book":"2Th","chapter":2,"verse":12,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" while obeying unrighteousness. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Co 12:20","book":"2Co","chapter":12,"verse":20},{"label":"Gl 5:20","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":20},{"label":"Php 2:3","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":3},{"label":"Jms 3:14","book":"Jas","chapter":3,"verse":14},{"label":"Jms 3:16","book":"Jas","chapter":3,"verse":16},{"label":"2Th 2:12","book":"2Th","chapter":2,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"There will be affliction and distress "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:35","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":35,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" for every human being who does evil, first to the Jew, and also to the Greek; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 3:26","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":26,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:16","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":16,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 4:17","book":"1Pe","chapter":4,"verse":17,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 8:35","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":35},{"label":"Ac 3:26","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":26},{"label":"Rm 1:16","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":16},{"label":"1Pt 4:17","book":"1Pe","chapter":4,"verse":17}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"but glory, honor, and peace for everyone who does what is good, first to the Jew, and also to the Greek. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For there is no favoritism with God. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 10:17","book":"Deu","chapter":10,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 10:34","book":"Act","chapter":10,"verse":34,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 10:17","book":"Deu","chapter":10,"verse":17},{"label":"Ac 10:34","book":"Act","chapter":10,"verse":34}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For all who sin without the law "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 9:21","book":"1Co","chapter":9,"verse":21,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" will also perish without the law, and all who sin under "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit in"},{"kind":"text","text":" the law will be judged by the law. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 9:21","book":"1Co","chapter":9,"verse":21}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit in"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For the hearers of the law "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 7:21","book":"Mat","chapter":7,"verse":21,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 7:24","book":"Mat","chapter":7,"verse":24,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 13:17","book":"Jhn","chapter":13,"verse":17,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 1:22","book":"Jas","chapter":1,"verse":22,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" are not righteous before God, but the doers of the law will be justified. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or acquitted"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 7:21","book":"Mat","chapter":7,"verse":21},{"label":"Mt 7:24","book":"Mat","chapter":7,"verse":24},{"label":"Jn 13:17","book":"Jhn","chapter":13,"verse":17},{"label":"Jms 1:22","book":"Jas","chapter":1,"verse":22}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Or acquitted"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So, when Gentiles, who do not by nature have the law, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 10:35","book":"Act","chapter":10,"verse":35,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:19","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":19,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" do "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":3,"text":"Or who do not have the law, instinctively do"},{"kind":"text","text":" what the law demands, they are a law to themselves even though they do not have the law. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 10:35","book":"Act","chapter":10,"verse":35},{"label":"Rm 1:19","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":19}],"footnotes":[{"marker":3,"text":"Or who do not have the law, instinctively do"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They show that the work of the law "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":4,"text":"The code of conduct required by the law"},{"kind":"text","text":" is written on their hearts. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 2:27","book":"Rom","chapter":2,"verse":27,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" Their consciences confirm this. Their competing thoughts either accuse or even excuse them "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":5,"text":"Internal debate, either in a person or among the pagan moralists"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 2:27","book":"Rom","chapter":2,"verse":27}],"footnotes":[{"marker":4,"text":"The code of conduct required by the law"},{"marker":5,"text":"Internal debate, either in a person or among the pagan moralists"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"on the day when God judges "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 10:42","book":"Act","chapter":10,"verse":42,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 17:31","book":"Act","chapter":17,"verse":31,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 3:6","book":"Rom","chapter":3,"verse":6,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 14:10","book":"Rom","chapter":14,"verse":10,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" what people have kept secret, according to my gospel through Christ Jesus. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 16:25","book":"Rom","chapter":16,"verse":25,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 15:1","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":1,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 1:11","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":11,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 1:11","book":"1Ti","chapter":1,"verse":11,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Tm 2:8","book":"2Ti","chapter":2,"verse":8,"letter":"i"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 10:42","book":"Act","chapter":10,"verse":42},{"label":"Ac 17:31","book":"Act","chapter":17,"verse":31},{"label":"Rm 3:6","book":"Rom","chapter":3,"verse":6},{"label":"Rm 14:10","book":"Rom","chapter":14,"verse":10},{"label":"Rm 16:25","book":"Rom","chapter":16,"verse":25},{"label":"1Co 15:1","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":1},{"label":"Gl 1:11","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":11},{"label":"1Tm 1:11","book":"1Ti","chapter":1,"verse":11},{"label":"2Tm 2:8","book":"2Ti","chapter":2,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now if "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss read Look—"},{"kind":"text","text":" you call yourself a Jew, and rely on the law, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mc 3:11","book":"Mic","chapter":3,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 5:45","book":"Jhn","chapter":5,"verse":45,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 9:4","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":4,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" and boast in God, "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mc 3:11","book":"Mic","chapter":3,"verse":11},{"label":"Jn 5:45","book":"Jhn","chapter":5,"verse":45},{"label":"Rm 9:4","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss read Look—"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"and know his will, and approve the things that are superior, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 1:10","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":10,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" being instructed from the law, "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Php 1:10","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"and if you are convinced that you are a guide for the blind, a light to those in darkness, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"an instructor of the ignorant, a teacher of the immature, having the embodiment of knowledge and truth "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 2:1–4","book":"Isa","chapter":2,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 42:6–7","book":"Isa","chapter":42,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 49:6","book":"Isa","chapter":49,"verse":6,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" in the law — "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 2:1–4","book":"Isa","chapter":2,"verse":1},{"label":"Is 42:6–7","book":"Isa","chapter":42,"verse":6},{"label":"Is 49:6","book":"Isa","chapter":49,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"you then, who teach another, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 23:3–7","book":"Mat","chapter":23,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" don’t you teach yourself? You who preach, “You must not steal” —do you steal? "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 23:3–7","book":"Mat","chapter":23,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You who say, “You must not commit adultery” —do you commit adultery? You who detest idols, do you rob temples? "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 19:37","book":"Act","chapter":19,"verse":37,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 19:37","book":"Act","chapter":19,"verse":37}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You who boast in the law, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mc 3:11","book":"Mic","chapter":3,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 5:45","book":"Jhn","chapter":5,"verse":45,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 9:4","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":4,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" do you dishonor God by breaking the law? "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or you dishonor God by breaking the law."},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mc 3:11","book":"Mic","chapter":3,"verse":11},{"label":"Jn 5:45","book":"Jhn","chapter":5,"verse":45},{"label":"Rm 9:4","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Or you dishonor God by breaking the law."}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For, as it is written: The name of God is blasphemed among the Gentiles because of you."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 52:5","book":"Isa","chapter":52,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 52:5","book":"Isa","chapter":52,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 36:20–23","book":"Ezk","chapter":36,"verse":20,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Pt 2:2","book":"2Pe","chapter":2,"verse":2,"letter":"d"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 52:5","book":"Isa","chapter":52,"verse":5},{"label":"Is 52:5","book":"Isa","chapter":52,"verse":5},{"label":"Ezk 36:20–23","book":"Ezk","chapter":36,"verse":20},{"label":"2Pt 2:2","book":"2Pe","chapter":2,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Circumcision benefits you if you observe the law, but if you are a lawbreaker, your circumcision has become uncircumcision. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 4:4","book":"Jer","chapter":4,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 9:25","book":"Jer","chapter":9,"verse":25,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 4:4","book":"Jer","chapter":4,"verse":4},{"label":"Jr 9:25","book":"Jer","chapter":9,"verse":25}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So if an uncircumcised "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 3:30","book":"Rom","chapter":3,"verse":30,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 7:19","book":"1Co","chapter":7,"verse":19,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 2:11","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":11,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" man keeps the law’s requirements, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:4","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":4,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" will not his uncircumcision be counted as circumcision? "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 3:30","book":"Rom","chapter":3,"verse":30},{"label":"1Co 7:19","book":"1Co","chapter":7,"verse":19},{"label":"Eph 2:11","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":11},{"label":"Rm 8:4","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"A man who is physically uncircumcised, but who keeps the law, will judge you "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 12:41","book":"Mat","chapter":12,"verse":41,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" who are a lawbreaker in spite of having the letter of the law and circumcision. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 12:41","book":"Mat","chapter":12,"verse":41}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For a person is not a Jew who is one outwardly, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 8:39","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":39,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 9:6","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 6:15","book":"Gal","chapter":6,"verse":15,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" and true circumcision is not something visible in the flesh. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 8:39","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":39},{"label":"Rm 9:6","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":6},{"label":"Gl 6:15","book":"Gal","chapter":6,"verse":15}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:2:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"On the contrary, a person is a Jew who is one inwardly, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 3:3","book":"Php","chapter":3,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 2:11","book":"Col","chapter":2,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" and circumcision is of the heart —by the Spirit, not the letter. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or heart —spiritually, not literally"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 7:6","book":"Rom","chapter":7,"verse":6,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 3:6","book":"2Co","chapter":3,"verse":6,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" That person’s praise is not from people but from God. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 5:44","book":"Jhn","chapter":5,"verse":44,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 12:43","book":"Jhn","chapter":12,"verse":43,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 4:5","book":"1Co","chapter":4,"verse":5,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 10:18","book":"2Co","chapter":10,"verse":18,"letter":"h"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Php 3:3","book":"Php","chapter":3,"verse":3},{"label":"Col 2:11","book":"Col","chapter":2,"verse":11},{"label":"Rm 7:6","book":"Rom","chapter":7,"verse":6},{"label":"2Co 3:6","book":"2Co","chapter":3,"verse":6},{"label":"Jn 5:44","book":"Jhn","chapter":5,"verse":44},{"label":"Jn 12:43","book":"Jhn","chapter":12,"verse":43},{"label":"1Co 4:5","book":"1Co","chapter":4,"verse":5},{"label":"2Co 10:18","book":"2Co","chapter":10,"verse":18}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or heart —spiritually, not literally"}]}]},"cachedAt":1783099531593}